					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load WLD_Main_A\r\n- Queue the DaisyDream1 camp night\r\n- After the camp night, perform a failed attack that should do damage.\r\n- Make sure neither you nor Daisy are in a dialogue.\r\n- This will play three times per user and then never again."
